00:17:33,510 --> 00:17:34,350
Jin Xia,

282
00:17:35,070 --> 00:17:36,380
I really envy you.

283
00:17:36,950 --> 00:17:39,720
If Nan Hua could be half as good to me as he is to you,

284
00:17:40,030 --> 00:17:42,270
