630
00:34:01,440 --> 00:34:02,760
Brother.

631
00:34:03,600 --> 00:34:04,400
What's wrong?

632
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:06,720
Nothing.

633
00:34:06,960 --> 00:34:07,760
Nothing?

634
00:34:08,120 --> 00:34:09,429
