671
00:36:06,720 --> 00:36:07,520
No, no.

672
00:36:07,680 --> 00:36:08,730
She will be fine.

673
00:36:09,040 --> 00:36:09,720
No.

674
00:36:11,640 --> 00:36:12,080
No.

675
00:36:27,960 --> 00:36:33,470
