689
00:38:19,320 --> 00:38:20,040
No.

690
00:38:20,440 --> 00:38:21,320
No.

691
00:39:24,520 --> 00:39:28,770
Grandma. Grandma.

692
00:39:36,120 --> 00:39:37,760
