734
00:42:34,360 --> 00:42:35,520
I know, Grandma.

735
00:42:36,200 --> 00:42:37,200
I promise you.

736
00:42:37,400 --> 00:42:39,640
I will live a happy life.

737
00:42:41,080 --> 00:42:42,680
